# NOTES
# =========================================
# 1. Test your site after implementing this .htaccess
# 2. Clear browser cache to see changes
# 3. Use online tools to verify GZIP is working
# 4. Some hosting providers may have different configurations
# 5. If you get a 500 error, comment out sections one by one
#    to find which directive is causing issues
